    "html": "<DOCUMENT>\n<TYPE>EX-99.1\n<SEQUENCE>2\n<FILENAME>vote.htm\n<DESCRIPTION>REPORT OF VOTING RESULTS\n<TEXT>\n<HTML>\n<HEAD>\n     <TITLE></TITLE>\n</HEAD>\n<BODY STYLE=\"font: 10pt Times New Roman, Times, Serif\">\n\n<P STYLE=\"margin: 0\"></P>\n\n<P STYLE=\"font: bold 10pt Calibri, Helvetica, Sans-Serif; margin: 0; text-align: right\"></P>\n\n<P STYLE=\"font: 8pt TradeGothic; margin: 0; letter-spacing: 1pt; text-align: right\"><IMG SRC=\"image_002.jpg\" ALT=\"\" STYLE=\"height: 61px; width: 153px\"></P>\n\n\n\n<P STYLE=\"font: bold 10pt Calibri, Helvetica, Sans-Serif; margin: 0; text-align: right\"></P>\n\n<P STYLE=\"font: bold 10pt Calibri, Helvetica, Sans-Serif; margin: 0\">VIA SEDAR</P>\n\n<P STYLE=\"font: 10pt Calibri, Helvetica, Sans-Serif; margin: 0; letter-spacing: 1pt\">&nbsp;</P>\n\n<P STYLE=\"font: 10pt Calibri, Helvetica, Sans-Serif; margin: 0; letter-spacing: 1pt\">To the Securities Regulatory Authorities:</P>\n\n<P STYLE=\"font: 10pt Calibri, Helvetica, Sans-Serif; margin: 0; letter-spacing: 1pt\">&nbsp;</P>\n\n<P STYLE=\"font: 10pt Calibri, Helvetica, Sans-Serif; margin-top: 0; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 0; letter-spacing: 1pt\"><B>RE:&#9;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Eldorado Gold Corporation (the &#8220;Company&#8221;)</B></P>\n\n<P STYLE=\"font: 10pt Calibri, Helvetica, Sans-Serif; margin-top: 0; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 0; letter-spacing: 1pt\"><B>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Report of Voting Results\npursuant to Section 11.3 of </B></P>\n\n<P STYLE=\"font: 10pt Calibri, Helvetica, Sans-Serif; margin-top: 0; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 0; letter-spacing: 1pt\"><B>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;National Instrument\n51-102 Continuous Disclosure Obligations (&#8220;NI-51-102&#8221;)</B></P>\n\n<P STYLE=\"font: 10pt Calibri, Helvetica, Sans-Serif; margin: 0; letter-spacing: 1pt\"><B>&nbsp;</B></P>\n\n<P STYLE=\"font: 10pt Calibri, Helvetica, Sans-Serif; margin: 0; letter-spacing: 1pt\">Following the Annual and Special Shareholders\nMeeting of the Company held on June 21, 2018 (the &#8220;Meeting&#8221;), and in accordance with Section 11.3 of NI51-102, we hereby\nnotify you of the following results obtained at the Meeting:</P>\n\n<P STYLE=\"font: 10pt Calibri, Helvetica, Sans-Serif; margin: 0; letter-spacing: 1pt; text-align: justify\">&nbsp;</P>\n\n<TABLE CELLSPACING=\"0\" CELLPADDING=\"0\" STYLE=\"width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse\">\n<TR STYLE=\"vertical-align: top\">\n    <TD STYLE=\"font: 10pt TradeGothic; padding-right: 5.4pt; padding-left: 5.4pt; letter-spacing: 1pt; text-align: center\">&nbsp;</TD>\n    <TD STYLE=\"font: 10pt TradeGothic; padding-right: 5.4pt; padding-left: 5.4pt; letter-spacing: 1pt; text-align: center\"><FONT STYLE=\"font: 10pt Calibri, Helvetica, Sans-Serif; letter-spacing: 0pt\"><B><I>Item Voted Upon</I></B></FONT></TD>\n    <TD COLSPAN=\"2\" STYLE=\"font: 10pt TradeGothic; padding-right: 5.4pt; padding-left: 5.4pt; letter-spacing: 1pt; text-align: center\"><FONT STYLE=\"font: 10pt Calibri, Helvetica, Sans-Serif; letter-spacing: 0pt\"><B><I>Voting Result</I></B></FONT></TD></TR>\n<TR STYLE=\"vertical-align: top\">\n    <TD STYLE=\"font: 10pt TradeGothic; padding-right: 5.4pt; padding-left: 5.4pt; letter-spacing: 1pt\"><FONT STYLE=\"font: 10pt Calibri, Helvetica, Sans-Serif; letter-spacing: 0pt\">1</FONT></TD>\n    <TD STYLE=\"padding-right: 5.4pt; padding-left: 5.4pt\">\n        <P STYLE=\"font: 10pt Calibri, Helvetica, Sans-Serif; margin: 0; letter-spacing: 1pt\"><FONT STYLE=\"letter-spacing: 0pt\">Election\n        of Directors</FONT></P>\n        <P STYLE=\"font: 10pt Calibri, Helvetica, Sans-Serif; margin: 0; letter-spacing: 1pt\"><FONT STYLE=\"letter-spacing: 0p